---
/**
 * about.astro — About Discover Texas
 * Route: /about
 */
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import scottImg from '../../images/scott-murray.jpg';
import jeniceImg from '../../images/jenice-murray.jpg';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Discover Texas"
  description="I'm Scott — a lifelong traveler who fell in love with Texas. This is the travel guide I wish existed."
>

<!-- ═══════════════ HERO ═══════════════ -->
<section class="about-hero">
  <video class="about-hero-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
    <source src="/videos/pillar/about-hero.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
  </video>
  <div class="about-hero-gradient-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="about-hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">About Discover Texas</div>
    <h1>One Texan at Heart, One Travel Guide Done <em>Right</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-intro">I'm Scott — a Southern California native who has been exploring Texas for years and fell in love with everything from Hill Country wine trails to Big Bend sunsets. After years of obsessive trip planning and countless road trips across the Lone Star State, I decided to build the travel guide I wished existed: real prices, honest recommendations, and none of the sponsored fluff.</p>
    <div class="hero-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ PERSONAL LETTERS ═══════════════ -->
<section class="letter-section reveal">
  <div class="letter-block">
    <div class="letter-attr">Scott <span class="attr-role">· Southern California native · Travel obsessive · Healthcare IT by day</span></div>
    <p class="letter-text">Travel has always been my escape from the rat race — and honestly, I enjoy the <strong>planning</strong> almost as much as being there. Researching destinations, mapping routes, finding that perfect small town with great BBQ and live music. Texas grabbed me on my first road trip through the Hill Country — the wide-open spaces, the friendliness of the people, the way a breakfast taco can change your entire morning.<br><br>I've driven every major highway in the state. I've waited in line at Franklin Barbecue. I've floated the Comal River. I've watched the sun set over Santa Elena Canyon in Big Bend and hiked Guadalupe Peak at sunrise. I've eaten my way through San Antonio's River Walk and discovered that the best Tex-Mex is never where the tourists are.<br><br><strong>I'm not a travel blogger. I work in healthcare IT.</strong> But Texas keeps pulling me back, and I finally decided to put everything I've learned into something useful — a site with real local knowledge, honest prices, video content from the places I've actually been, and an AI trip planner that builds itineraries from real travel experience. It's the resource I wished existed when I planned my first Texas road trip.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ TIMELINE ═══════════════ -->
<section class="timeline-section">
  <div class="timeline-header">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Our Story</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">How This Started</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline">
    <div class="tl-item reveal">
      <div class="tl-year-side"><div class="tl-year">First Trip</div></div>
      <div class="tl-dot"></div>
      <div class="tl-content-side"><div class="tl-content">
        <div class="tl-title">Hill Country Road Trip</div>
        <p class="tl-text">My first real Texas road trip: Austin to Fredericksburg, wine tasting on the 290 trail, live music at Luckenbach. I realized Texas was unlike anywhere I'd been — the scale, the friendliness, the food. The addiction begins.</p>
      </div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item reveal">
      <div class="tl-year-side"><div class="tl-year">Going Deeper</div></div>
      <div class="tl-dot"></div>
      <div class="tl-content-side"><div class="tl-content">
        <div class="tl-title">Beyond the Big Cities</div>
        <p class="tl-text">Marfa, Big Bend, Palo Duro Canyon, Caddo Lake. Each trip goes further from the tourist trail. I discover that the best of Texas isn't in Dallas or Houston — it's in the small towns, the state parks, and the roads in between.</p>
      </div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item reveal">
      <div class="tl-year-side"><div class="tl-year">Documenting</div></div>
      <div class="tl-dot"></div>
      <div class="tl-content-side"><div class="tl-content">
        <div class="tl-title">Capturing Texas</div>
        <p class="tl-text">I start documenting everything — video from canyons, BBQ joints, river floats, and desert highways. The idea crystallizes: why does no Texas travel site show you what these places actually look and feel like?</p>
      </div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item reveal">
      <div class="tl-year-side"><div class="tl-year">2025</div></div>
      <div class="tl-dot"></div>
      <div class="tl-content-side"><div class="tl-content">
        <div class="tl-title">Discover Texas Launches</div>
        <p class="tl-text">The travel guide I wished existed finally becomes real — with video content, an AI trip planner, and honest recommendations from real experience. Not a side hustle with recycled content. A real guide built by someone who loves this state.</p>
      </div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ PROFILE CARDS ═══════════════ -->
<section class="profiles-section">
  <div class="profiles-header">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Meet the Team</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">The People Behind the Pages</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="profiles-grid">
    <div class="profile-card reveal">
      <div class="profile-banner scott"><div class="profile-banner-bg"></div></div>
      <Image src={scottImg} alt="Scott Murray" class="profile-avatar scott-av" width={96} height={96} format="webp" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="profile-body">
        <div class="profile-name">Scott</div>
        <div class="profile-role">Co-founder · Writer · Videographer</div>
        <p class="profile-bio">Healthcare IT professional by day, Texas travel obsessive by every other waking moment. Based in Southern California. Enjoys the trip planning almost as much as the travel itself. Has driven every major Texas highway, eaten at BBQ joints across the state, floated the rivers, and hiked the canyons.</p>
        <div class="profile-stats">
          <div class="profile-stat"><div class="profile-stat-num">59</div><div class="profile-stat-label">TX destinations covered</div></div>
          <div class="profile-stat"><div class="profile-stat-num">9</div><div class="profile-stat-label">Regions explored</div></div>
          <div class="profile-stat"><div class="profile-stat-num">40+</div><div class="profile-stat-label">Countries traveled</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-card reveal">
      <div class="profile-banner jenice"><div class="profile-banner-bg"></div></div>
      <Image src={jeniceImg} alt="Jenice Murray" class="profile-avatar jenice-av" width={96} height={96} format="webp" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="profile-body">
        <div class="profile-name">Jenice</div>
        <div class="profile-role">Co-founder · Local Expert · Cultural Perspective</div>
        <p class="profile-bio">Filipina by birth, world traveler by marriage. Jenice brings a fresh outsider perspective to Texas travel — someone who notices what locals take for granted and asks the questions that visitors actually want answered. Her love of food, festivals, and genuine local culture shapes the recommendations that make this site different from every generic Texas travel guide.</p>
        <div class="profile-stats">
          <div class="profile-stat"><div class="profile-stat-num">20+</div><div class="profile-stat-label">Years traveling</div></div>
          <div class="profile-stat"><div class="profile-stat-num">Pampanga</div><div class="profile-stat-label">Hometown</div></div>
          <div class="profile-stat"><div class="profile-stat-num">Real</div><div class="profile-stat-label">Local insights</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ OUR PROMISE ═══════════════ -->
<section class="promise-section">
  <div class="promise-inner">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Our Promise</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">What You'll Never Find Here</h2>
    <p class="promise-text">I built this site because I got tired of Texas travel content that's secretly a press trip recap or a sponsored hotel review dressed up as honest advice. Discover Texas exists because I wanted the resource I wished existed when I planned my first road trip.</p>
    <div class="zero-grid">
      <div class="zero-card reveal"><div class="zero-num coral">0</div><div class="zero-label">Sponsored posts<br><em>ever</em></div></div>
      <div class="zero-card reveal"><div class="zero-num teal">0</div><div class="zero-label">Press trips or<br>free hotel stays</div></div>
      <div class="zero-card reveal"><div class="zero-num gold">59</div><div class="zero-label">Destinations<br>covered</div></div>
      <div class="zero-card reveal"><div class="zero-num white-num">100%</div><div class="zero-label">Real prices in<br>USD</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="promise-quote">If I recommend it, I've been there. If I list a price, I've paid it. If I tell you to skip something, I've wasted my own money there first. This is a truthful, fact-based site.</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ WHAT WE'RE BUILDING ═══════════════ -->
<section class="vision-section">
  <div class="vision-inner">
    <div class="vision-content">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">What We're Building</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">More Than a Travel Blog</h2>
      <p class="vision-text">Discover Texas isn't a collection of "Top 10" listicles. It's a living resource built on real travel experience and technology that actually helps you plan a better trip. Here's what makes it different:</p>
      <ul class="vision-list">
        <li><span class="v-icon">🎥</span> Video guides for select destinations — see the canyons, towns, and beaches before you book</li>
        <li><span class="v-icon">🤖</span> An AI trip planner that builds custom itineraries with real prices, not hallucinated estimates</li>
        <li><span class="v-icon">💰</span> Every price listed in USD, updated regularly based on what I actually pay</li>
        <li><span class="v-icon">🗺️</span> 59 destinations across 9 regions — from the Gulf Coast to the Panhandle</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a href="/plan/" class="btn-primary">✦ Try the AI Trip Planner</a>
        <a href="/destinations/" class="btn-outline">Browse All Destinations</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="vision-features">
      <a href="/destinations/" class="v-feature reveal"><div class="v-feature-icon">🤠</div><div class="v-feature-title">Destination Guides</div><div class="v-feature-desc">Deep dives into 59 Texas destinations — not surface-level overviews, but real logistics and insider tips.</div></a>
      <div class="v-feature reveal"><div class="v-feature-icon">📹</div><div class="v-feature-title">Video Content</div><div class="v-feature-desc">Real footage from Big Bend, the Hill Country, the Gulf Coast, and more. See it before you go.</div></div>
      <a href="/plan/" class="v-feature reveal"><div class="v-feature-icon">🗺️</div><div class="v-feature-title">AI Trip Planner</div><div class="v-feature-desc">Describe your dream trip and get a custom day-by-day itinerary built on real Texas travel experience.</div></a>
      <div class="v-feature reveal"><div class="v-feature-icon">📧</div><div class="v-feature-title">Itinerary Downloads</div><div class="v-feature-desc">PDF itineraries you can take offline — complete with maps, booking links, and insider tips.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ EMAIL CTA ═══════════════ -->
<section class="email-cta-section">
  <div class="email-cta-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title">Get the Guide Before Everyone Else</h2>
    <p class="email-cta-desc">We're building new destination guides, video content, and trip planner features every month. Drop your email and we'll send the good stuff first — no spam, no affiliate dumps, just real Texass travel intel from two people who actually go there.</p>
    <form class="email-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();">
      <input type="email" class="email-input" placeholder="your@email.com" />
      <button type="submit" class="btn-sand">Subscribe →</button>
    </form>
    <p class="email-note">We respect your inbox. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<script>
  if (!window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches) {
    const ro = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
      entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible'); });
    }, { threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' });
    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => ro.observe(el));
  } else {
    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => el.classList.add('visible'));
  }
</script>

<style>
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     HERO
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .about-hero {
    padding: 160px 24px 100px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(165deg, #141C26 0%, #172830 30%, #1a3035 55%, #172830 75%, #141C26 100%);
  }
  .about-hero-video {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .about-hero-gradient-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 40%, rgba(0,0,0,0.55) 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  @keyframes orbFloat {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
    33% { transform: translate(20px, -15px); }
    66% { transform: translate(-10px, 10px); }
  }
  .hero-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }
  .about-hero-inner {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-warm-gold);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) forwards 0.2s;
  }
  .about-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.5vw, 3.8rem);
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) forwards 0.4s;
  }
  .about-hero h1 em {
    color: var(--color-warm-gold);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .hero-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) forwards 0.6s;
  }
  .hero-intro em {
    color: var(--color-warm-gold);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .hero-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 56px;
    margin: 48px auto 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(212,165,116,0.5), transparent);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) forwards 0.9s;
  }
  @keyframes heroUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     PERSONAL LETTERS
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .letter-section {
    padding: 80px 24px 64px;
    max-width: var(--content-lg);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .letter-block {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 32px;
    border-left: 2px solid #EBE4D8;
    margin-bottom: 52px;
    transition: border-color 0.5s ease;
  }
  .letter-block:hover { border-left-color: var(--color-ocean-teal); }
  .letter-block:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .letter-attr {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-warm-coral);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .letter-attr .attr-role {
    color: #718096;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .letter-text {
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--color-deep-night);
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .letter-text strong { font-weight: 600; }
  .letter-text em { font-style: italic; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     TIMELINE
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .timeline-section {
    padding: 80px 24px 100px;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }
  .timeline-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: var(--content-lg);
    margin: 0 auto 72px;
  }
  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-warm-coral);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    color: var(--color-deep-night);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .timeline {
    max-width: var(--max-width, 1120px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #EBE4D8, var(--color-ocean-teal), var(--color-warm-coral), var(--color-warm-gold), #EBE4D8);
  }
  .tl-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    position: relative;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .tl-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 3px solid var(--color-ocean-teal);
    z-index: 2;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .tl-item:hover .tl-dot {
    background: var(--color-warm-coral);
    border-color: var(--color-warm-coral);
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.35);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(232,101,74,0.15);
  }
  .tl-year {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    color: #EBE4D8;
    line-height: 1;
    transition: color 0.5s ease;
  }
  .tl-item:hover .tl-year { color: var(--color-ocean-teal); }
  .tl-content { max-width: 420px; }
  .tl-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-deep-night);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .tl-text {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-slate);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .tl-item:nth-child(odd) .tl-year-side { text-align: right; }
  .tl-item:nth-child(odd) .tl-content-side { text-align: left; padding-left: 12px; }
  .tl-item:nth-child(even) { direction: rtl; }
  .tl-item:nth-child(even) > * { direction: ltr; }
  .tl-item:nth-child(even) .tl-year-side { text-align: right; }
  .tl-item:nth-child(even) .tl-content-side { text-align: left; padding-left: 12px; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     PROFILE CARDS
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .profiles-section {
    padding: 100px 24px;
    background: var(--color-sand);
  }
  .profiles-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: var(--content-lg);
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
  }
  .profiles-grid {
    max-width: var(--max-width, 1120px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .profile-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(26,35,50,0.08);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1), box-shadow 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
  }
  .profile-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(26,35,50,0.14);
  }
  .profile-banner { height: 200px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .profile-banner-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; transition: transform 0.8s ease; }
  .profile-card:hover .profile-banner-bg { transform: scale(1.08); }
  .profile-banner.scott {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0c3547 0%, #0D7377 40%, #14B8A6 70%, #38D9A9 100%);
  }
  .profile-banner.jenice {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #78350F 0%, #D4A574 40%, #FBBF24 70%, #FDE68A 100%);
  }
  .profile-banner::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle 80px at 25% 35%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent),
      radial-gradient(circle 60px at 75% 65%, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), transparent);
  }
  .profile-avatar {
    width: 96px;
    height: 96px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 4px solid var(--color-white);
    margin: -48px auto 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    object-fit: cover;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .profile-card:hover .profile-avatar { transform: scale(1.08); }
  .profile-avatar.scott-av { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D7377, #14B8A6); }
  .profile-avatar.jenice-av { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4A574, #FBBF24); }
  .profile-body { padding: 20px 32px 32px; text-align: center; }
  .profile-name {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-deep-night);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .profile-role {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    color: #718096;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .profile-bio {
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    color: var(--color-slate);
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-weight: 300;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .profile-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 32px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-sand);
  }
  .profile-stat { text-align: center; }
  .profile-stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    color: var(--color-deep-night);
  }
  .profile-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.63rem;
    color: #718096;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     OUR PROMISE
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .promise-section {
    padding: 100px 24px;
    background: var(--color-deep-night);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .promise-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 900px;
    height: 900px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(13,115,119,0.05), transparent 55%);
